task.summary: Default task
Added the visible FOV to the minimap. Made some really nice changes to the overworld and cleaned up minimap colors.
Fixing the death screen modal...
Fixed death screen modal and added a 'play again' button. Added cute tombstone ascii art for death
Still working on ladders
Added rats, fixed death screen, made sure that changing between overworld and dungeons saves player location
Working on items and changing the inheritance for actors

Added sword, weapon, item, entity classes. Made some sword objects and made every goblin drop one on death. Introduced new bug that makes invincible goblins if attacked over a sword...? Introduced unicode characters (testing)
Squashed the bug with undying/undamaging goblins. Weird problem with JS array pop method vs shift
Quick fix to the map
Fixed minimap exploration for dungeons. Overworld is always revealed and dungeons are always hidden until explored.
Separated all of the entities into separate files and directories. Starting to look more like a Java project than a JavaScript one.
Cleaned up file hierarchy again. Combined actor, entity, and item
Added a little bit of a user guide in the README.md. Playing with some new fonts and cleaning up inventory system UI. Squashing bugs!
